WEBVTT

00:00.059 --> 00:01.798
<i>Previously
on Shades of Blue...</i>

00:02.000 --> 00:03.165
<i>I heard shots.
They sounded real.</i>

00:03.168 --> 00:04.599
<i>A video game?</i>

00:04.602 --> 00:06.200
I got to make this right.

00:06.203 --> 00:07.969
<i>Neighborhood's raising money
to bury the man I killed.</i>

00:07.971 --> 00:09.737
- This a friend of yours?
- My cousin.

00:09.740 --> 00:11.173
<i>You donated a lot of money.</i>

00:11.175 --> 00:12.807
Want you all to know
that I'm sorry, all right?

00:12.810 --> 00:14.442
Let's go.

00:14.445 --> 00:16.745
- Crooked-ass police.
- Yeah.

00:16.746 --> 00:17.980
Murderers.

00:17.981 --> 00:20.214
There's a rat on my team.

00:20.216 --> 00:22.115
I told you, I'm gonna start
looking at everyone.

00:22.117 --> 00:23.350
Portuguese, right?

00:23.353 --> 00:25.152
But when I realized
the escort was Brazilian,

00:25.155 --> 00:26.786
<i>I asked her to teach me
how to say a few things.</i>

00:26.789 --> 00:28.789
Far as Wozniak knows,
we were together all morning.

00:28.791 --> 00:32.826
Saperstein said he was with
Tufo when he spotted your guy.

00:33.628 --> 00:35.496
Why are you hiding the mail?

00:35.499 --> 00:37.531
<i>The man you're framing,
Miguel Zepeda,</i>

00:37.533 --> 00:40.399
<i>the paper trail
leads right back to you.</i>

00:40.402 --> 00:43.070
He threatened to kill me,
and I knew he would.

00:44.323 --> 00:47.570
Sync and corrections by n17t01
www.addic7ed.com

00:52.515 --> 00:54.481
Let's go.

